  Gin2-na2 kio3 ¡§Chhai5-long5.¡¨ 
  Bat u7 chit8 e5 chhi7-iuN5 e5 gin2-na2, li7-khui hiuN-sia7 bo5 joa7 hng7 teh kou3 i e5 iuN5-kun5. U7 chit8 pai2 i siuN7 i beh piN3 chit8 e5 kau5-lang7 lai5 chhong3-ti7 hiuN-sia7 e5 lang5. Sou2-i2 i chau2 kau3 sia7-nih8 toa7 siaN chhut-lat8 kio3 kong2, ¡§Chhai5-long5 ouh ! Chhai5-long5 ouh ! Lai5 pang-chan7 goa2 ! Chhai5-long5 beh lai5 ka7 iuN5 lah !¡¨ 
  Chiah-e5 ho2 sim e5 lang5 chiu7 pang3 in e5 kang chau2 lai5 chhan5-nih8 pang-chan7 i. Chong2-si7 in kau3 e5 si5, chit e5 gin2-na2 tit8-tit8 chhio3 in e5 tioh8-boa5 ; bo5 chhai5-long5 ti7 hia. 
  Koh chit8 jit8 chit e5 gin2-na2 koh an2-ni chhong3-ti7 in, chiah-e5 hiuN-sia7 lang5 chau2 lai5 pang-chan7 i, koh hou7 i chhio3. 
  Au7-lai5 u7 chit8 jit8, chit8 chiah chhai5-long5 thiah jip8 chit e5 iuN5-tiau5, beh hai7 si2 iuN5-a2. Gin2-na2 toa7 kiaN chiu7 chau2 beh kio3 pang-chan7, toa7 siaN ki-ki kio3 kong2, ¡§Chhai5-long5 ! Chhai5-long5 ! U7 chit8 chiah chhai5-long5 ti7 iuN5-nih8, Pang-chan7 ouh !¡¨ 
  Chiah-e5 hiuN-sia7 lang5 thiaN-kiN3, phah-sng3 si7 koh teh la5-eng5, bo5 chit8 e5 u7 chit8-tiam2-a2 ti3-i3 a2-si7 khah kun7-oa2 i. Sou2-i2 chit e5 chhi7-iuN5 gin2-na2 sit-loh8 long2-chong2 e5 iuN5. 
  Lang5 siong5-siong5 kong2 peh8-chhat8 kau3 tu2-tioh8 tai7-chi3 e5 si5, kong2 chin-sit8 bo5 lang5 beh sin3 i. 
  Kong2 sit8 oe7 e5 thang ku2-tng5, kong2 peh8-chhat8 e5 liam5-piN pai7. Chim-gian5 12 chiuN 19 chat. 
  Chhan5-kap-a2 Ong5 
  Li2 bat thiaN-kiN3 gong7 chhan5-kap-a2 e5 ku7 kou3-su7 bo5 ? U7 koa2 chhan5-kap-a2 ti7 chit8 e5 chui2-khut saN-kap tiaN7-tioh8 in tioh8 chit8 e5 ong5. In siong5-siong5 chiau5-chng5 peng5-an keng-ke3 long2 bo5 ong5. Chong2-si7 in hut-jian5-kan tiaN7-tioh8 sim-chi3 tioh8 u7 chit8 e5 ong5. In chhe chit8 e5 su3-chia2 kau3 ti7 Sin5-beng5 hia, lai5 kiu5 i chhe chit8 e5 ong5 lai5 koan2-li2 in. 
  Sin5-beng5 khoaN3 in si7 chin7 gong7, iah8 chhe chit8 e5 ong5 boe7 hai7 in, i hiat chit8 te3 chha5-thau5 ti7 tham5-a2 lai7. 
  Phiak8 chit8 e7 chhan5-kap-a2 chin7 kiaN, chng3 jip8 in e5 khang khi3 bih, li7-khui Chha5-thau5 Ong5. 
  Chong2-si7 chit8 tiap8-a2 ku2 khoaN3-kiN3 hit e5 ong5 boe7 tin2-tang7, in kiaN5 ke3, chiu7 khi3 che7 ti7 i teng2-bin7. Koh bo5 joa7-ku2 in khoaN3-kiN3 sit8-chai7 boe7 hai7 in, chiu7 khoaN3-khin i, lou7-be2 in koh chhe chit8 e5 su3-chia2 khi3 chhe7 Sin5-beng5, chhiaN2 i koh chhe chit8 e5 sin e5 ong5. 
  Sin5-beng5 chhe chit8 be2 sian7-hi5
  Chiah-e5 Chhan5-kap-a2 si7 chin7 hoaN-hi2, iah8 chin7 kiaN Sian7-hi5 Ong5 teh leng3, teh siu5 ti7 in e5 tiong-kan. Chong2-si7 jit8 ke3 jit8, khoaN3 sian7-hi5 long2 bo5 hai7 in, chiu7 bo5 kiaN. In bo5 kiaN Sian7-hi5 Ong5 e5 si5, chiu7 bo5 kiong-keng3 i. 
  Bo5 joa7-ku2 in koh chhe chit8 e5 su3-chia2 kau3 Sin5-beng5 hia, kiu5 i hou7 in chit8 e5 khah ho2 e5 ong5, khah u7 lou7-eng7 e5 ong5. 
  Sin5-beng5 lou7-be2 siu7-khi3 in e5 gong7. I kong2, ¡§Goa2 beh hou7 lin2 chit8 e5 ong5, tu2-tu2 chiau3 lin2 sou2 ai3 e5.¡¨ I chiu7 hou7 in chit8 chiah peh8-hoh8. Chiah-e5 chhan5-kap-a2 liam5-piN kau3 ti7 chui2-bin7, lai5 chheng2-an sin e5 ong5, Peh8-Ong5 eng7 i e5 chhui3-chiam tok in, ka7 in thun-lun loh8-khi3. 
  In chit8 chiah chit8 chiah bok8 khi2-lai5, peh8-hoh8 chiu7 chit8 chiah chit8 chiah chiah8 loh8-khi3. 
  I chin-chiaN3 oe7 kham-tit choe3 in e5 ong5. 
  (1)Mng7. Chhan5-kap-a2 ai3 tit-tioh8 oe7 hai7 in e5 ong5 tioh8 a2 m7 tioh8 ? Si7 chin7 gong7 e5 sou2 siuN7. 
  (2)Chhan5-kap-a2 Ong5, chaiN2-iuN7 khoan2-thai7 chhan5-kap-a2 ? Chit8 chiah chit8 chiah thun loh8-khi3. 
  Pou7-giok8 e5 kun-ong5, ap-che3 song3-hiong lang5, chhin-chhiuN7 hau2 e5 sai, chhe7 chiah8 e5 him5. Chim-gian5 28 chiuN 15 chat. 
  Jit8 kap Hong
  U7 chit8 pai2 jit8 kap hong teh saN-chiN chi7-chui7 khah iong2. Tak8 e5 sin3 i ka-ki7 khah u7 lat8. In teh pian7-pok e5 si5, khoaN3-kiN3 chit8 e5 kiaN5-lou7 e5 lang5 teh kiaN5 chiuN7 chit8 e5 hiuN-sia7, chheng7 chit8 nia2 toa7 saN. 
  Hong chiu7 kong2. TaN u7 ki-hoe7 thang lai5 chhi3 lan2 e5 lat8. Lai5 khoaN3 lan2 ta2-loh8 chit8 e5 kau3-giah8 u7 lat8 thang hou7 chit e5 kiaN5-lou7 e5 lang5 thng3 i e5 saN, hit e5 oe7 an2-ni choe3, chiu7 oe7 seng5-jin7 si7 khah u7 lat8. 
  Jit8 chiu7 kong2, ¡§Thang eng7 an2-ni choe3 iok.¡¨ 
  Chit8 tiap8-a2 ku2 hong chiu7 chhe, chit e5 lang5 e5 saN phu7-phu7 pe, iah8 chit8 toa7 chun7 e5 phauh8 kap hou7 phah i. Chong2-si7 i na2 loh8, na2 leng2 chit e5 kiaN5-lou7 e5 lang5 na2 nih8 i e5 saN khah an5 lai5 ui5 i. Hong boe7-oe7 hou7 I thng3 khi3. 
  TaN si7 tioh8 jit8 lah ! I chiu7 sia7 i long2-chong2 e5 kng-soaN3 ti7 chit e5 lang5 e5 keng-thau5. Na2 ku2 na2 joah8, chit e5 lang5 thng3-khui i e5 saN, au7-lai5 hian ti7 au7-bin7, lou7-be2 chiu7 thng3 khi2-lai5, an2-ni Jit8 tit-tioh8 iaN5. 
  (1)Mng7. Kong5-hong chaiN2-iuN7 boe7 hou7 lang5 thng3 saN ? Eng7 kiong5-hong si7 khang-khang tioh8-boa5. 
  (2)Jit8 chaiN2-iuN7 oe7 hou7 lang5 thng3 saN ? Eng7 nng2 hoat chiu7 lang5 oe7 sun7-hok8. 
  Kong2 oe7 un-jiu5, hou7 lang5 siau-khi3 siu7-khi3, gian5-gu2 kiong5-ok hou7 lang5 kek-khi3 siu7-khi3. Chhim-gian5 15 chiuN 1 chat. 
  Soe3 chiah Long5 kap Gok8-hi5
  Soe3 chiah long5 put-chi2 ai3 chiah8 u7 khak e5 chui2-chok8. I siong5-siong5 tui3 khoe-piN loh8-khi3, tui3 piN-a2 un5-a2 chhe7 chim5-chhih8 hit ho7 e5 lui7. U7 chit8 pai2 i teh chhe7 chim5 e5 si5, chin iau, i chhun i e5 chhiu2-chiuN2 beh jih8 chit8 chiah chim5, bo5 tai7-seng siong5-se3 khoaN3 e7-toe2 si7 sim2-mih8. 
  Tng i chhun i e5 chhiu2-chiuN2 hap8 chit8 e5 e5 si5, chit8 chiah toa7 e5 gok8-hi5 ti7 thou5-be5 lai7 ka7 tioh8 i e5 chhiu2-chiuN2. 
  Soe3 chiah long5 chiu7 siuN7 kong2, ¡§TaN chham2 ! Chit chiah toa7 chiah e5 gok8-hi5 ka7 goa2 e5 chhiu2-chiuN2 ti7 i e5 chhui3. Koh chit8 tiap8-a2 ku2 i beh thoa goa2 khi3 ka7 goa2 thun loh8-khi3. 
  Goa2 taN beh chaiN2-iuN7 choe3 ? Beh chaiN2-iuN7 choe3 ?¡¨ 
  I chiu7 hut-jian5-kan siuN7 kong2, ¡§Goa2 beh phian3 i.¡¨ 
  I chiu7 eng7 put-chi2 hoaN-hi2 e5 siaN chhin-chhiuN7 long2 bo5 tai7-chi3, kong2, ¡§Oh hoh ! Chin7 gau5 e5 Gok8-hi5 Sian-siN ! Chhang-mia5 e5 Gok8-hi5 Sian-siN ! Li2 phah-sng3 hit e5 lou7-ui5 kun si7 goa2 e5 chhiu2-chiuN2 houN7 ! Goa2 ng3-bang7 li2 chiah8 liau2 chin7 nng2.¡¨ 
  Chit chiah lau7 e5 gok8-hi5 bih ti7 thou5-be5 kap lou7-ui5 hioh8 e5 e7-bin7, bo5 khoaN3-kiN3 poaN3 hang7, I siuN7 kong2, ¡§Chheh ! Goa2 si7 sit-chho3 lah !¡¨ Sou2-i2 i khui i e5 chhui3 pang3 soe3 chiah long5 khi3. 
  Soe3 chiah long5 chiau3 i sou2 oe7 e5 kin2, chau2 khi3. I chau2 e5 si5 kio3 kong2, ¡§To-sia7, Gok8-hi5 Sian-siN ! Ho2 sim e5 Gok8-hi5 Sian-siN ! Li2 chin7 ho2 sim pang3 goa2 khi3.¡¨ 
  Chit chiah lau7 gok8-hi5 sut i e5 be2, beh koh hap8 i e5 e7-hoai5, chong2-si7 siuN oaN3, soe3 chiah long5 hou7 i ka7 boe7 tioh8 . 
  Au7-lai5 chit chiah soe3 chiah long5 chau2 li7-khoe un2-tang3. Chong2-si7 chha-put-to koh chit8 le2-pai3, chin7 ai3 chiah8 chim5 e5 long5, bo5 pat8 mih8 thang hou7 i ke3-gian3. I chai-kio3 i tek-khak tioh8 chiah8 chim5. Sou2-i2 koh loh8-khi3 khoe-piN si3-ui5 put-chi2 soe3-ji7 khoaN3. I bo5 khoaN3-kiN3 lau7 gok8-hi5, chong2-si7 i ka-ki7 siuN7. ¡§Goa2 siuN7 goa2 m7-ai3 tu2-tioh8 kan-khou2.¡¨ Sou2-i2 i khia7 tiaN7-tiaN7 toa7 siaN kong2, ¡§Goa2 long2 bo5 khoaN3-kiN3 soe3 chiah chim5 ti7 chit e5 sou2-chai7, goa2 siong5-siong5 khoaN3-kiN3 in thong2 chhut-lai5 ti7 chui2-nih8. Goa2 chiu7 chhun goa2 e5 chhiu2-chiuN2 lai5 liah8 in. Goa2 teh siuN7 kin-a2-jit8 m7 chai u7 teng7 e5 soe3 chiah chim5 ti7 chui2-nih8 bo5 ?¡¨ 
  Chit chiah lau7 e5 gok8-hi5 bih ti7 khoe-toe2 e5 thou5-be5, thiaN-kiN3 soe3 chiah long5 kong2 e5 si5, i siuN7 ¡§Oh hoh ! Goa2 beh ke2-choe3 soe3 chiah chim5. I chhun i e5 chiuN2 jip8 lai5 e5 si5, goa2 chiu7 ka7 i liah8 lai5 chiah8.¡¨ 
  Sou2-i2 i kiah8 i e5 ou-be2 e5 phiN7 ti7 chui2-teng2 lai5 theng3-hau7. 
  Soe3 chiah long5 khoaN3 chit8 e7 chiu7 kong2, ¡§Gok8-hi5 Sian-siN, to-sia7 ! Ho2 sim e5 Gok8-hi5 Sian-siN ! Li2 si7 kek8 ho2 sim lai5 hou7 goa2 khoaN3 li2 si7 ti7 hia ! Goa2 beh khi3 pat8 ui7 chiah8 !¡¨ I chiu7 chau2 chhin-chhiuN7 hong hiah kin2. 
  Chit chiah lau7 gok8-hi5 bu7 pheh8 ti7 chhui3-nih8, chin siu7-khi3, chong2-si7 soe3 chiah long5 khi3 lah. 
  Koh nng7 le2-pai3 ku2, soe3 chiah long5 long2 bo5 lai5 khoe-nih8. Au7-lai5 u7 chit8 jit8, pak-tou2 lai7 tong3 boe7 tiau5 chi2 u7 chim5 oe7 hou7 i peng5-an, i chai i te7-it chio2 tioh8 u7 chit8 chiah chim5 thang chiah8. I chiu7 chin7 soe3-ji7 loh8-khi3 khoe-nih8 si3-ui5 khoaN3. 
  I khoaN3 bo5 lau7 gok8-hi5 e5 ki3-ho7. 
  Chong2-si7 i m7-ai3 tu2-tioh8 kan-khou2. Sou2-i2 i khia7 chin7 tiaN7, ka-ki7 kong2-oe7, chiau3 I peng5-siong5 e5 khoan2-sit. I kong2, ¡§Goa2 long2 bo5 khoaN3-kiN3 soe3 chiah chim5 ti7 hoaN7-nih8, a2-si7 thong2 chhut-lai5 ti7 chui2-nih8, goa2 peng5-siong5 khoaN3 in pun5 phok8-a2 tui3 chui2-e7 khi2-lai5. Chiah-e5 soe3 e5 phok8-a2 phu3, phu3, phu3, au7-lai5 bok8, bok8, bok8, hou7 goa2 chai soe3 chiah chim5 ti7 ta2-loh8. Sou2-i2 goa2 oe7 chhun goa2 e5 chhiu2-chiuN2 jip8-khi3 liah8 i. Goa2 teh siuN7 kin-a2-jit8 m7 chai oe7 khoaN3-kiN3 soe3 e5 phok8-a2 boe7 ?¡¨ 
  Lau7 gok8-hi5 bih ti7 thou5-be5 kap chui2-chhau2 e7-toe2 thiaN-kiN3 an2-ni, i siuN7, ¡§Chhih ! He si7 chin7 khoai3, goa2 beh lai5 pun5 soe3 e5 chim5 phok8-a2, iah8 i chiu7 beh chhun i e5 chhiu2-chiuN2 jip8-lai5, goa2 oe7 liah8 tioh8 i.¡¨ 
  Sou2-i2 pun5, koh pun5 chin7 toa7 lat8 ; chiah-e5 phok8-a2 khi2 kau3 chin choe7 chhi7-chhi7 kun2. 
  Soe3 chiah long5 m7 bian2 lang5 ka7 i kong2 si7 chi7-chui7 teh chhong3 hiah-e5 phok8-a2, ia7 ka-ki7 oe7 chai. I koaN2-kin2 khoaN3 chit8 e7 choe3 i chau2-khi3. 
  Chong2-si7 i khi3 e5 si5, na2 gim5 kong2, ¡§To-sia7 li2, Gok8-hi5 Sian-siN ! Ho2 sim e5 Gok8-hi5 Sian-siN ! Li2 si7 ti7 se3-kan te7 it ho2 sim e5 Gok8-hi5, lai5 hou7 goa2 khoaN3 li2 ti7 ta2-loh8, chin7 ho2 ! Goa2 beh khi3 pat8 sou2-chai7 e5 khoe chiah8 cha2-khi2 tng3.¡¨ 
  Chit chiah lau7 gok8-hi5 chin7 siu7-khi3, sou2-i2 pe5 chiuN7 hoaN7-nih8 khi3 jip soe3 chiah long5, chong2-si7 kho2-sioh i liah8 boe7 tioh8, in-ui7 i chau2 chin7 kin2. 
  Chit e5 tai7-chi3 liau2-au7, soe3 chiah long5 m7 kaN2 koh mou7-hiam2 khi3 kun7 chui2, sou2-i2 bo5 koh chiah8 chim5. Chong2-si7 i chhe7-tioh8 chit8 e5 hng5 u7 ia2 bu5-hoa-ko2, chin7 ho2 chiah8, i tak8 jit8 khi3 hia lai5 chiah8. 
  TaN chit e5 gok8-hi5 chha5 chai, i tiaN7 tioh8 giau5 gi5 e5 soe3 chiah long5 ! Goa2 beh hou7 chiah-e5 bu5-hoa-ko2 tin2-tang7, i chiu7 oe7 phah-sng3 si7 hong chhe in.¡¨ I liam5-piN ka-ki7 chheng3-khi2-lai5, iah8 tin2-tang7, hou7 chiah-e5 soe3 bu5-hoa-ko2 phun3-khi2-lai5, i e5 ka-chiah chiu7 khoaN3 kiN3-kiN3. 
  Soe3 chiah long5 bo5 theng3-hau7 koh khoaN3 chit8 e7. I chau2 chhin-chhiuN7 hong hiah kin2. Chhut-hng5 chong2-si7 i chau2 e5 si5, tui3 au7-bin7 kio3, Gok8-hi5 Sian-siN, koh-chai3 to-sia7 li2, li2 put-chi2 ho2 lai5 hou7 goa2 khoaN3 li2 ti7 hia. Goa2 boe7 oe7 chiau3 goa2 sou2 ai3, theng5 teh ka7 li2 kong2 to-sia7. Li2 chhiaN2 !¡¨ 
  An2-ni chit e5 lau7 gok8-hi5 siu7-khi3 kau3 kong5. I chiu3-choa7 bo5 lun7 chaiN2-iuN7 chit8 pai2 beh chiah8 chit8 chiah long5. Sou2-i2 i pe5, so5 tui3 toe7-nih8 khi3 kau3 ti7 soe3 chiah long5 e5 chhu3, pe5, so5 jip8 ti7 lai7-bin7 bih ti7 chhu3-lai7, theng3-hau7 soe3 chiah long5 to3-lai5. 
  Bo5 joa7 ku2 soe3 chiah long5 na2 thiau3 to3-lai5, hoaN-hi2, bo5 khoa3-lu7, chi2-u7 si3-ui5 khoaN3. Tu2-tu2 i lai5 e5 si5 i khoaN3-kiN3 chit e5 thou5-kha long2 si7 jiau3 e5 hun5, chhin-chhiuN7 u7 chin7 tang7 e5 mih8 thoa ke3-khi3. Soe3 chiah long5 theng5 teh khoaN3, kong2, ¡§He si7 sim2-mih8 ! He si7 sim2-mih8 !¡¨ 
  I chiu7 khoaN3-kiN3 i e5 chhu3 e5 mng5, u7 khoeh8 tioh8 piN-a2 iah8 phoa3, tu2-tu2 chhin-chhiuN7 u7 put-chi2 toa7 e5 mih8 ke3-khi3. Soe3 chiah long5 kong2, ¡§Che si7 sim2-mih8 ! Che si7 sim2-mih8 ! Goa2 siuN7 goa2 beh chha5-kho2 teh !¡¨ 
  Sou2-i2 i khia7 tiaN7-tiaN7 ka-ki7 kong2-oe7, (Li2 oe7 ki3-tit i peng5-siong5 sou2 choe3) Chong2-si7 i toa7 siaN kong2, ¡§Chin7 ki5-koai3, goa2 e5 soe3 keng chhu3 bo5 ka7 goa2 kong2. Soe3 keng Chhu3, chaiN2-iuN7 li2 bo5 ka7 kong2 ? Goa2 to3-lai5 e5 si5 tak8 hang7 e5 mih8 long2 ho2-se3 li2 siong5-siong5 ka7 goa2 kong2. Goa2 teh siuN7 goa2 e5 soe3 keng chhu3 u7 sim2-mih8 tai7-chi3.¡¨ 
  Chit e5 lau7 gok8-hi5 siuN7 i tek-khak tioh8 ke2 choe3 soe3 keng chhu3 ; na7 bo5 soe3 chiah long5 bo5 beh jip8-lai5. Sou2-i2 i chiau3 i sou2 oe7 e5 kek chit8 e5 chin7 ho2 e5 siaN, (M7 bian2 kong2 li2 iah8 chai) kong2, ¡§Ouh, soe3 chiah long5 !¡¨ 
  Ai ah ! soe3 chiah long5 thiaN-kiN3 hit e5 e5 si5, i chit8 e7 chin7 kiaN kau3-kek8. I kong2, ¡§Si7 lau7 gok8-hi5. Goa2 chit pai2 bo5 kap i kiat-be2, i tek-khak beh hou7 goa2 kiat-kiok8. Goa2 beh chaiN2-iuN7 choe3 ?¡¨ 
  I koaN2-kin2 siuN7, chiu7 i kong2 chin7 ho2 thiaN. I kong2, ¡§Soe3 keng chhu3, to-sia7 li2, chin7 hoaN-hi2 thiaN-kiN3 li2 ho2 thiaN e5 siaN. Sou2 thiaN3 e5 soe3 keng chhu3, goa2 chit8 tiap8-a2 ku2 chiu7 beh jip8-lai5. Chong2-si7 goa2 tioh8 khioh koa2 chha5 thang chu2 e7-tau3.¡¨ 
  I chiu7 khi3 khioh chha5, khioh chin choe7. Iah8 tui chin chat8 ti7 mng5-nih8, ui5 chit keng chhu3 ; chiah pang3 he2 sio. 
  He2 tit8-tit8 chheng3 ian, iah8 sio kau3 lau7 gok8-hi5 chiaN5 choe3 hun e5 hi5. 
  (1)Mng7. Gok8-hi5 chaiN2-iuN7 piN3-choe3 hun hi5 ? In-ui7 ke3-bou5 beh chiah8 soe3 chiah long5. 
  Sou2-i2 tek-khak chiah8 ka-ki7 kiat e5 ke2-chi2, chhiong-moa2 ka-ki7 siat e5 ke3-bou5, gong7 lang5 poe7 to7-li2 tek-khak hai7 ka-ki7 e5 sin-khu. Chim-gian5 1 : 31-32. 
